
Version 0.1.17, 2010-04-08

    Fixes: BMC#556 - Show screen brightness slider depending on gconf value
    Fixes: MB#477 - [REG] "All Settings" do not open in the front screen
    Fixes: MBC#427 - No way to access or empty trash from panel
    l10n: Updates to sv, fi, pl, pt_BR, es, zh_CN

Version 0.1.16, 2010-04-06

    Fixes: MBC#497 - Wrong arguments used for launching banshee

Version 0.1.15, 2010-04-02

    Add simple brightnes tile.

Version 0.1.14, 2010-04-01

    More work on the new visual design.
    Remove udisks dependency.
    Switch to using external importers.
    l10n: Lots of translation update.

Version 0.1.13, 2010-03-30

    Depend on mx-1.0 >= 0.9, fix for API changes
    Adapt to new visual design (still lacking a few assets).
    Fixes: BMC#266 -- Stray definitions of MnbToolbarButton base style in css
    l10n: Lots of translation update.

Version 0.1.12, 2010-03-25

    Depend on mx-1.0 >= 0.9, fix for API changes
    l10n: Updates to Brazilian Portuguese (pt_BR) translation

Version 0.1.11, 2010-03-22

    Depend on mx-1.0 >= 0.8
    l10n: Updates to Chinese (Taiwan) translation
    l10n: Updates to Polish (pl) translation
    l10n: Updates to Swedish (sv) translation
    l10n: Updates to Japanese (ja) translation
    l10n: Updates to Finnish (fi) translation
    l10n: Updates to Korean (ko) translation
    l10n: Updates to Russian (ru) translation

Version 0.1.10, 2010-03-04

    Add moving label to the volume tile.
    Add volume change notification sound.

Version 0.1.9, 2010-03-02

    Load storage device icons from gtk icon theme.
    Escape device mount point and open using gtk_show_uri().
    Increase panel height to allow for 2 devices without scrolling.

Version 0.1.8, 2010-02-26

    Implement support for pluggable storage devices.
    Hook up to XF86XK_Sleep key.
    Use C types where applicable.

Version 0.1.7, 2010-02-17

    Pull global stuff into panel class.
    Add infrastructure for pluggable devices tiles.
    Code and build system cleanups.

Version 0.1.6, 2010-02-16

    Robust handling of DK's singleton objects.
    i18n: Share strings between panel and power-icon.
    Handle double press of power button.
    Set X-Moblin-Panel-Button-Style for the toolbar capplet.
    Pull global stuff into power-icon class.
    Fixes: MB#7852 Closing notebook lid during shutdown results in sleep mode.

Version 0.1.5, 2010-02-15

    Port over low battery notifications from dalston.
    Implement suspend on lid close.
    Various code and build system cleanups.
    Fixes: MB#9673 (0.1.4)

Version 0.1.4, 2010-02-12

    Implement power icon.
    Integrate new assets.
    Various build system tweaks.

Version 0.1.3, 2010-02-09

    Update visual appearance.
    Fixes: MB#9536
    Port over idle time handling from dalston.
    Build system cleanups.

Version 0.1.2, 2010-02-08

    Update visual appearance.

